org.eclipse.gef

Class AccessibleEditPart

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.draw2d.AccessibleBase
      • org.eclipse.gef.AccessibleEditPart
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractGraphicalEditPart.AccessibleGraphicalEditPart

    public abstract class AccessibleEditPart
extends AccessibleBase
    This class provides Accessibility support for EditParts. EditParts are the unit of selection in GEF. When selection changes, Accessibility clients are notified. These clients then query the EditPartViewer for various accessibility information.

    EditParts must provide AccessibileEditPart adapters in order to work with screen-readers, screen magnifiers, and other accessibility tools. EditParts should override AbstractEditPart.getAccessibleEditPart().
